Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.91,0:00:30.82,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'd sort of casually met
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.91,0:00:30.82,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nanigenaku deatta
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.82,0:00:33.72,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gathering kindness together
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.82,0:00:33.72,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yasashisa yoseatte
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.49,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The hide-and-seek continues
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.49,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kakurenbo wa tsuzukuno
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.49,0:00:37.16,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.49,0:00:37.16,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sou sa
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.16,0:00:40.26,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, wanna sell your soul
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.26,0:00:42.93,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With a fancy yellow touch
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.26,0:00:42.93,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shareta kiiroi tatchi de
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.93,0:00:46.26,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, forget smile again
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.26,0:00:50.53,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to be dancing always
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.26,0:00:50.53,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Itsumo odotteitai dake
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.67,0:00:55.67,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, chase me, chase me
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.67,0:00:55.67,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nee oikakete oikakete
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.67,0:00:57.54,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White breeze
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.67,0:00:57.54,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroi kaze
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.54,0:01:01.85,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I want it to be a crush, then love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.54,0:01:01.85,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nee koi ni natte ai ni natte
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.85,0:01:03.38,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to spread my wings
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.85,0:01:03.38,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hane hirogetai
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.38,0:01:07.25,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, take the good things and the bad
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.38,0:01:07.25,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nee ii koto mo warui koto mo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.25,0:01:09.19,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Add them all together
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.25,0:01:09.19,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Subete tashite
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.19,0:01:13.73,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Divide it by two and live well
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.19,0:01:13.73,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ni de watte umaku ikite
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.73,0:01:21.66,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to transcend time
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.73,0:01:21.66,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toki o koetai
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.52,0:02:12.68,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eiri...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.26,0:02:25.75,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeš za to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.60,0:02:30.93,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je to moja chyba.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.71,0:02:41.98,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ako to, že Eiri odpadol?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.62,0:02:47.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Touma?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.09,0:02:50.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč Mika, je to moja chyba.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.53,0:02:56.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bad Luck práve oznámili\Nsvoje plánované turné...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.83,0:03:00.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a Sakuma Ryuichi zo skupiny Nittle\NGrasper im prišiel pogratulovať...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.03,0:03:02.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...k ich prvému albumu, z ktorého\Nsa predalo vyše milión kusov.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.83,0:03:05.36,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V celej sále zavládla veľká radosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.84,0:03:09.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uvidíme, čím nás táto nová úspešná\Nskupina prekvapí opäť v budúcnosti!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.18,0:03:11.51,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To je všetko, vraciam slovo do štúdia.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.51,0:03:12.61,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To je všetko, vraciam slovo do štúdia.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.51,0:03:18.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milión kópii... už to\Nnie je len sen, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.62,0:03:21.98,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, už to nie je sen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.52,0:03:26.51,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gratulujem, boli ste výborní!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.83,0:03:29.85,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A to nám hovorí niekto,\Nkto predal 2 milióny za 2 dni...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.40,0:03:32.86,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Musím to ihneď oznámiť Yukimu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.47,0:03:34.97,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Láskyplný ako vždy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.97,0:03:36.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A čo ty Hiro,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.30,0:03:37.77,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,nejdeš to náhodou oznámiť Ayake?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.77,0:03:40.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? N-No, tak by som to nenazval...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.11,0:03:41.44,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HCFCFCF&}OK, telefón, telefón.{\c&HFFFFFF&}\NČo? N-No, tak by som to nenazval...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.44,0:03:41.81,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? N-No, tak by som to nenazval...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.81,0:03:44.61,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poviem jej to po telefóne,\Nnebudem predsa cestovať do Kjóta.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.61,0:03:47.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie že by som sa s ňou nechcel stretnúť...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.25,0:03:49.01,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej! Počúvaj, keď sa s tebou niekto rozpráva!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.95,0:03:53.98,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shuichi, niekto ti volal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.15,0:03:56.65,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bol to Yuki?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.65,0:03:58.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ktovie či sledoval našu konferenciu?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.32,0:04:01.29,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Gratulujem. Tvrdo si pracoval."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.69,0:04:02.73,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Také niečo by on...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.73,0:04:03.50,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HCFCFCF&}Také niečo by on...{\c&HFFFFFF&}\NZdá sa, že Yuki vykašľal krv, odviezli ho do nemocnice.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.86,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa, že Yuki vykašľal krv, odviezli ho do nemocnice.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.43,0:04:12.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keď sa to dopočuje, asi tiež odpadne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.94,0:04:14.73,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skoro aj ja.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.54,0:04:16.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bol to šok.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.88,0:04:19.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Žeby si o mňa mala starosti?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.88,0:04:22.40,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samozrejme! Som tvoja sestra!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.42,0:04:27.28,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vykašľať krv kvôli\Nstresu je dobrý námet na príbeh.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.75,0:04:29.12,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Som predsa autor...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.75,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To stačí, Eiri.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.19,0:04:33.16,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tváriť sa tak ľahostajne\Npo tom, čo sa stalo...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.86,0:04:36.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vieš predsa, kvôli\Nčomu sa ti to stalo...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.27,0:04:45.33,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Neutekajte po chodbách, prosím.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.74,0:04:47.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ak Yuki vykašľal krv,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.37,0:04:49.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}musí mať vážnu chorobu
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a už je v poslednom štádiu a...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.11,0:04:50.54,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a už je v poslednom štádiu a...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.91,0:04:51.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nemôže predsa...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.51,0:04:53.53,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nie!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.41,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To nie!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.78,0:04:57.44,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nezaujíma ma nejakých milión albumov!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.85,0:04:59.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bože, prosím!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.22,0:05:01.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Uesugi Eiri
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.86,0:05:11.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eiri, bude lepšie, ak sa\Nnebudeš stýkať so Shindom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.83,0:05:14.92,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Môžeš svoje romány písať\Nv Amerike, alebo Európe, nie?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.93,0:05:17.73,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,New York nie je zlý nápad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.07,0:05:20.26,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pochybujem, že by tam za mnou cestoval.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.17,0:05:24.54,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Najlepší liek je\Nzbaviť sa stresu...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.54,0:05:29.04,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem kritizovať\Ntvoj vzťah so Shindom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.08,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale v tvojom súčasnom stave,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.08,0:05:33.05,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bude lepšie, ak sa mu budeš vyhýbať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.05,0:05:34.28,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Asi hej.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.65,0:05:37.85,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Možno bude lepšie,\Nak sa rozídeme natrvalo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.33,0:05:43.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eiri, vyrovnáš sa s tým?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.93,0:05:47.12,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.54,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shuichi...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.74,0:05:55.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Už si späť? Ako je Yukimu?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.21,0:05:57.41,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki je nažive.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.41,0:05:59.60,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, to je mi jasné, ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.98,0:06:00.81,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idem domov.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.75,0:06:04.15,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki ochorel kvôli mne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.98,0:06:06.68,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy som na to ani nepomyslel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.32,0:06:10.58,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Netušil som, že Yuki\Ntrpí, keď je so mnou.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.66,0:06:13.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kvôli mne je Yuki...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.46,0:06:14.56,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vedel som to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.56,0:06:15.08,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vedel som to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.63,0:06:18.56,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V poslednom čase mi to bolo divné.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bývať so Shuichim pod jednom strechou...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.83,0:06:22.60,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To chce odvahu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.94,0:06:26.07,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, nemaj obavy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.27,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki si na to časom zvykne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.27,0:06:31.47,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Navyše, ak by ťa nemal rád,\Nuž dávno by odišiel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.92,0:06:39.94,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak predsa?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.72,0:06:46.42,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Na! Pozor, je horúce.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.76,0:06:56.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mal by si nad tým prestať dúmať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.36,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.24,0:07:01.51,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak by som si uvedomil skôr,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.51,0:07:04.50,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,že som Yukimu na obtiaž,\Nnemusel takto trpieť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.97,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vždy so mnou jedná ako s hlupákom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.71,0:07:09.01,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.81,0:07:11.61,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...nikdy som to tak nebral.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.28,0:07:14.88,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nestalo sa to predsa prvýkrát.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.25,0:07:17.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Určite mu rozumieš viac,\Nnež ktokoľvek iný.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.66,0:07:23.92,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki je láskavý. To je možno dôvod,\Nprečo ma neodmietol.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.10,0:07:28.62,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Si hlupák?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.53,0:07:32.66,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kto by to s tebou vydržal\Nkvôli láskavosti?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.34,0:07:34.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otrava.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.71,0:07:37.41,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je zase?! To som tak na obtiaž?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.41,0:07:38.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prekážka v ceste?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.64,0:07:40.45,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zodratá guma, ktorá sa nedá používať?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.45,0:07:42.98,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vypálená žiarovka?! Deravá ponožka?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.05,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Neplatný kupón?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.05,0:07:45.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mokrá pyrotechnika?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.72,0:07:47.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dáždnik bez rebier?!\NAuto bez motora?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.39,0:07:49.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gitara bez strún?!\NPonorka bez vody?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Opäť si vo svojej nálade.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.73,0:08:00.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nedúmaj nad tým,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,zbytočne sa budeš trápiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.74,0:08:05.27,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ale Yuki...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.27,0:08:07.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sú to skutočne Yukiho práve city?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.61,0:08:11.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mal by si ich počuť\Npriamo od neho.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, ak ti to predsalen nevýjde,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.68,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,som tu pre teba.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.31,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prejdem priamo k veci.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.86,0:08:27.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nepáči sa mi rozchod Yuki\NEiriho so Shindom Shuichim.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.83,0:08:29.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Z akého dôvodu?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.36,0:08:32.19,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eiriho už nepotrebujete.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.66,0:08:35.57,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím, že vám s propagáciou\Npomohol viac než dosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.93,0:08:37.26,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, ešte nie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.77,0:08:39.87,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pomohol nám len získať\Npozornosť širokej verenosti...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.87,0:08:41.93,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a predať milión albumov.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.24,0:08:44.14,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Práve sme začali.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.14,0:08:46.47,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz je dôležité, aby Shindo\Ndostal svoju odmenu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.78,0:08:47.15,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Uesugi Eiri
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Uesugi Eiri
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ste skutočne dobrý manažér.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.71,0:08:51.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takých ľudí si cením.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.22,0:08:56.08,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale, trvám na tom,\Naby sa Eiri a Shindo rozišli.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.15,0:09:25.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem aby si šiel preč.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.22,0:09:29.45,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale už vôbec nechcem,\Naby si trpel kvôli mne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.99,0:09:32.15,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Preto...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.32,0:09:34.45,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Preto?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.83,0:09:39.50,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dočerta...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.50,0:09:42.56,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Si hore? Prečo si to nepovedal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nezvyčajné...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.37,0:09:47.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...pre niekoho kto vždy trval na svojom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.51,0:09:51.01,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.01,0:09:52.07,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aj ty.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.41,0:09:55.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Asi predsalen pôjdem do New Yorku.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.75,0:10:03.85,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak si sa rozhodol odísť,\Nnemôžem ťa zastaviť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.49,0:10:07.58,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale... Ale ja...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.43,0:10:10.19,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zomriem, ak ma tu necháš.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.46,0:10:13.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Možno ti spôsobujem stresy,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ale z toho predsa neumrieš, nie?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ja by som bez teba neprežil!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.07,0:10:19.00,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je mi jedno, či vykašliavaš krv...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.00,0:10:20.40,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...alebo máš dieru v bruchu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.48,0:10:26.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Neber to tak výžne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.25,0:10:31.27,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak nie si úprimný,\Nje s tebou nuda.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.62,0:10:33.85,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Navyše, ak by si mi\Nbol len na obtiaž,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.82,0:10:37.01,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,nikdy by som ťa k sebe nepustil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.66,0:10:38.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.69,0:10:41.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Po pravde,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.59,0:10:45.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,keď som s tebou, neustále mám v hlave zmetok.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.90,0:10:50.10,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akoby som mal v hlave niečo,\Nna čo chcem zabudnúť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.37,0:10:53.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Žiť, alebo zomrieť,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.41,0:10:56.60,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,zas tak zlé to nie je.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.68,0:11:00.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A vidíš, mali sme sľub.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.35,0:11:05.58,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sľúbil som, že ťa zoberiem na rande,\Nak predáte milión albumov, spomínaš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.72,0:11:08.12,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takže!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.32,0:11:11.35,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shindo zajtra ide na rande!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.19,0:11:14.59,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, viem ako sa cítiš.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.23,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ešte si si neužil s Ayakov.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.23,0:11:18.59,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chlape, nezávidím ti!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.46,0:11:21.23,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je to v poriadku? Zachviľú máme koncert!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.57,0:11:24.33,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej. Každý potrebuje z času na čas oddych.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.87,0:11:27.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bude to pre Shinda dobrá motivácia.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.64,0:11:29.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím, že je mu to jedno,\Npokiaľ má svojho Yukiho...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.18,0:11:34.54,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rande! Rande! Rande!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.95,0:11:37.44,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fajn, ďakujem za spoluprácu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.68,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Díky aj vám!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.69,0:11:44.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mám ešte nejaké povinnosti, takže...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.72,0:11:46.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jasne, Touma, veľa šťastia!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.56,0:11:50.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Musíš to mať ťažké,\Nvykonávať i funkciu prezidenta.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.10,0:11:54.06,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ani nie. Celkom si to užívam.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.77,0:12:03.90,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Máš čas sa tu takto poflakovať?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.21,0:12:06.21,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa, že Touma je pracovitejší ako ty.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.65,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, K!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.15,0:12:09.65,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ako sa máš?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.58,0:12:15.58,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Len ma trápi jedna vec.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.79,0:12:18.31,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Týka sa to Toumy, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, si bystrá.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poznám ho už dosť dlho.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.83,0:12:26.50,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Usmieva sa... Ale mám\Npocit, že je naštvaný.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.06,0:12:28.27,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak predsa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.84,0:12:34.54,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ten váš spevák...\Nnevyviedol mu niečo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.37,0:12:37.34,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bohužial, nemôžem to vylúčiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.84,0:12:39.14,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mýlite sa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.71,0:12:42.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Touma nie je naštvaný,\Nje smutný!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.88,0:12:43.87,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuichi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.45,0:12:46.52,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Možno ho bolí bruško...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.42,0:12:53.08,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Už som myslela,\Nže konečne povie niečo múdre.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.59,0:12:57.19,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, to od neho nemôžme čakať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.73,0:12:59.20,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, rozumiem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.80,0:13:03.56,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Musíš predsa tušiť,\Nčo má Touma zaľubom!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.97,0:13:07.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ja s tým nič neurobím,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.84,0:13:10.53,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,môžem sa len pozerať, ako trpíte.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.13,0:13:30.03,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Seven days
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.03,0:13:31.60,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tangled up in gloom
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.60,0:13:33.23,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Seven days
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.23,0:13:35.20,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.20,0:13:37.03,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Seven days
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.03,0:13:38.74,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Going perfectly nowhere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.74,0:13:40.37,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Seven days
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.37,0:13:42.40,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A nightmarish seven days
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.65,0:13:59.96,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry,\Nnothing to be troubled about
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.96,0:14:03.62,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dandy's doing a handstand
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.76,0:14:07.23,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no choice but to settle it tonight
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.23,0:14:10.63,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Erase my memories, after the dream
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.14,0:14:18.01,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's beginning, the seven days
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.01,0:14:25.35,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I can take a peek, that'd be great
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.35,0:14:26.82,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Seven days
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.82,0:14:29.02,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let me sleep too much
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.02,0:14:30.45,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Seven days
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.45,0:14:32.22,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hard work, sun
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.22,0:14:34.23,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Seven days
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.23,0:14:36.16,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be in quicksand soon
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.16,0:14:37.63,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Seven days
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.63,0:14:39.93,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A gloomy seven days
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.27,0:14:47.67,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nádherné!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.65,0:14:57.94,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skutočne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.62,0:15:00.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je to ako sen,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.49,0:15:03.68,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sami dvaja na rande.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.78,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A bol si ku mne taký milý.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.26,0:15:10.46,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vravel som, že dnes urobím,\Nčo budeš chcieť. Spomínaš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.10,0:15:13.56,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keď už som tak milý,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.97,0:15:18.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,prezradím ti to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.07,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Čo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.14,0:15:31.01,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chýbajúcu časť mojej minulosti.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.82,0:15:41.92,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To si... ty, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.46,0:15:43.76,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Správne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.75,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A tá osoba vedľa mňa je človek...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.76,0:15:49.46,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ktorého som zabil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.94,0:15:55.80,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Volal sa Kitazawa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.51,0:15:58.53,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bol mojím tútorom v New Yorku.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.81,0:16:09.68,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mal som ťažké detstvo, lebo farba\Nmojích vlasov a očí je v Japonsku veľmi netypická.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.35,0:16:14.22,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seguchi si to všimol\Na zobral ma do New York.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.79,0:16:17.23,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tam ma s ním zoznámil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.66,0:16:18.99,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pán Kitazawa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.57,0:16:27.20,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Veľmi sa mi páčil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.21,0:16:30.67,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vždy sa usmieval a bol milý.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.51,0:16:34.81,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zbožňoval som ho,\Nako staršieho brata. Ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.07,0:16:59.59,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeš za to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.94,0:17:02.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.21,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je to moja chyba.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.81,0:17:10.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nespomínam si presne,\Nčo sa stalo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.18,0:17:14.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keď som sa spamätal,\Nbol tam Seguchi
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.82,0:17:17.34,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a ja som... plakal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.63,0:17:23.75,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, tá osoba...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.20,0:17:30.53,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mimochodom, Kitazawové\Nprvé meno bolo "Yuki".
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.54,0:17:34.13,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Odtiaľ pochádza moje literárne meno, Yuki.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.64,0:17:40.61,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz poznáš moje tajomstvá.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.01,0:17:42.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Si šťastný?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.41,0:17:44.75,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chcel si to vedieť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.65,0:17:50.95,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Som rád.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.42,0:17:54.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.73,0:18:01.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, idem kúpiť niečo na pitie!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.24,0:18:09.61,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo budem robiť?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.20,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bol to strašný príbeh!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.68,0:18:18.41,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki to vravel tak kľudne,\Nakoby to ani nebola pravda...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.28,0:18:22.51,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale keď nad tým premýšľam,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.99,0:18:27.58,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki sa s tým už pravdepodobne zmieril.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.53,0:18:30.46,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale prečo mi to všetko povedal...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.40,0:18:35.92,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Žeby ma... miloval?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.42,0:18:54.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pán učiteľ!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.59,0:19:01.42,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Som rád, že som\Nvás spoznal, pán Kitazawa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.33,0:19:04.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Budeme vždy spolu, však?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.94,0:19:22.34,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Predsalen...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.48,0:19:25.00,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neviem si spomenúť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.76,0:19:38.66,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tieto pocity, stále im nerozumiem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.53,0:19:45.33,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč, Yuki.
